cat << EOF
The OpenCA Project is a collaborative effort to develop a robust, full-featured
and Open Source out-of-the-box Certification Authority implementing the most
used protocols with full-strength cryptography world-wide. OpenCA is based on
many Open-Source Projects. Among the supported software is OpenLDAP, OpenSSL,
Apache Project, Apache mod_ssl.
